Third-party source and test material
------------------------------------

The repository retains selected upstream TypeScript source and public test
fixtures under tests/UpstreamSources/. These files remain under Apache-2.0 and
are checksum-pinned by tests/UpstreamSources/source-file-checksums.txt.

Additional JSON fixtures under tests/Fixtures/ are either:

  - extracted from the pinned tkhq/sdk test files; or
  - generated by tests/Fixtures/Generators/ from the exact npm versions above.

Each fixture records its source or generator provenance. Values that resemble
private keys, credentials, mnemonics, or signed payloads are public upstream
test vectors only; they are not live credentials and must never be reused as
secrets.
